query:
SELECT se.id, se.studentId, se.subjectId, se.professorId, s.id as subject_id_check, s.name as subject_name, s.userId as subject_userId
FROM student_enrollments se 
LEFT JOIN subjects s ON se.subjectId = s.id AND se.professorId = s.userId
WHERE se.studentId = 1
LIMIT 5;
